{
  "stem": "2830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she put me down on a chair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she told the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cook.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was also Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they all, you know, helped each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They all had good positions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were fluent in German and-- you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And she put me down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said to give me an apron to cover the wounds, my feet, and to give me a-- a bowl of, you know, potatoes to peal.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, like I work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, you have to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're finished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, and she told her to give me and the-- when they-- in those kettles where there-- that soup, that mishmash is.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To take out if there is a little bit of meat or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the bottom-- if, you  know, to bring me once in awhile.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That cook, she did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a-- a while to eat a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt, you know, every day a little better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the, you know, pus was, you know, it was still bleeding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My feet were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were getting better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Better, because the swelling keeps going down, then I didn't had that pain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I couldn't just sit like this constantly with the potatoes make believe I peel it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said to me, I started-- I knew by myself that I have to help myself, or I'm  dead here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what did you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I'm going to help like that carrying out those kettles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, four woman it takes, you know, to grab those kettles--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-and carry out, two in the front and two in the back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and one of that I know, the girls that I knew from Birkenau, she said she knew my condition.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
